      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/170/5724",
      "text": [
        " : \" اَلْمُسْلِمُ يَحْجُبُ اَلْكَافِرَ وَ يَرِثُهُ وَ اَلْكَافِرُ لاَ يَحْجُبُ اَلْمُؤْمِنَ وَ لاَ يَرِثُهُ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5724 - Al-Hasan ibn Mahbub narrated from Al-Hasan ibn Salih from Abu Abdullah Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) who said:\n\"A Muslim prevents a disbeliever from inheriting and inherits from him, but a disbeliever neither prevents a believer from inheriting nor does he inherit from him.\""
        ]
      }
